{"tid":676932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"若為自由故","createTime":"2018-05-24T18:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T19:11:31.000Z","uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba42ea3e170e69258a3dd1ba65171b71a0b839a7","tid":676932,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:55:06.000Z","msg":"「因為敵人就在眼前」<br />\n<br />\n「把眼前的敵人驅逐後就可以獲得和平嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n我錯了。真正的敵人並不是如此簡單。<br />\n<br />\n猶大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合理嗎？<br />\n<br />\n一切皆可拋。"},{"pid":"d26ba5a824ae88c109d2ac5d050bcb471076978f","tid":676932,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T18:55:15.000Z","msg":"「寧化飛灰，不作浮塵。<br />\n寧投熊熊烈火，光盡而滅；<br />\n不伴寂寂朽木，默然同腐。<br />\n寧為耀目流星，迸發萬丈光芒；<br />\n不羨永恒星體，悠悠沉睡終古。」"},{"pid":"61230cfe00647dbabf37759a492e246cccaa8081","tid":676932,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"吱"},{"pid":"da8b4137294211a7e9ae65431addfbc2337882ae","tid":676932,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61230cfe00647dbabf37759a492e246cccaa8081","tid":676932,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"吱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:10:16.000Z","msg":"你終於來了 等了你很久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027edd2581e84f15a922b90e6bb03ddc9e8cdba6","tid":676932,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da8b4137294211a7e9ae65431addfbc2337882ae","tid":676932,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61230cfe00647dbabf37759a492e246cccaa8081","tid":676932,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"吱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:10:16.000Z","msg":"你終於來了 等了你很久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T19:11:31.000Z","msg":"訓啦 夜"}]}